            <h1>Performance Excellence Policy</h1>
            <div class="meta-info">
                <span><i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i> Effective: February 5, 2026</span> | 
                <span><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> Authority: N.C.G.S. § 126-4</span>
            </div>
