                    <h3>Questions?</h3>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <span class="faq-question">How often should I meet?</span>
                        <small>At least quarterly, or whenever you need support.</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <span class="faq-question">What if I disagree with my rating?</span>
                        <small>You can request a formal review through your agency's process.</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <span class="faq-question">Can ratings affect pay?</span>
                        <small>Yes. Ratings are used for pay, promotions, and recognition.</small>
                    </div>
